WEBVTT

00:01.369 --> 00:03.237
ADULT ADAM: Back in the '80s,
my life changed forever

00:03.304 --> 00:05.139
when I saw the movie
Weird Science.

00:05.206 --> 00:07.041
For a geek like me,
nothing was cooler

00:07.108 --> 00:09.943
than two social
outcasts using their
tricked-out computer

00:10.010 --> 00:11.779
to create a magical
dream-woman.

00:11.845 --> 00:13.214
Was it absurd?
Sure.

00:13.281 --> 00:15.283
Did it stop me?
No.

00:15.349 --> 00:18.586
(ADAM CHANTING GIBBERISH)

00:24.658 --> 00:27.995
By the way, why are we
wearing bras on our heads?

00:28.062 --> 00:29.063
Ceremonial.

00:29.130 --> 00:30.431
Cut.
So how'd we do?

00:30.498 --> 00:32.200
May I just point out
how incredibly flawed

00:32.266 --> 00:33.901
the gender politics
of all of this is?

00:33.967 --> 00:35.103
Please don't judge me.

00:35.169 --> 00:36.504
I just have
an unhealthy desire

00:36.570 --> 00:38.072
to live in each and every
John Hughes movie.

00:38.139 --> 00:39.607
I'm just hoping
this actually works

00:39.673 --> 00:41.642
and we magically create
a foxy babe for me
to smooch on.

00:41.709 --> 00:44.011
Wait, you do realize
none of this is real.

00:44.078 --> 00:45.146
Let Dave Kim have this.

00:45.213 --> 00:46.547
Show time.

00:46.614 --> 00:47.748
(KNOCK ON DOOR)

00:48.882 --> 00:50.218
It worked?

00:52.052 --> 00:53.287
Yes!
I built an Erica.

00:53.354 --> 00:54.955
Hey, weirdos.
I'm leaving for college

00:55.022 --> 00:56.824
in 30 minutes,
and I need my bras.

00:56.890 --> 00:59.127
Ew!
I put it on my head!

00:59.193 --> 01:01.529
You told me these belonged
to your grandma.

01:01.595 --> 01:03.397
Which is not much better
now that I saw it out loud.

01:03.464 --> 01:04.698
Okay, I'm off to college.

01:04.765 --> 01:08.001
Adam, I'll miss you.
Dave Kim, the opposite.

01:08.068 --> 01:09.470
You keep telling
yourself that.

01:09.537 --> 01:11.038
(GAGS)

01:11.105 --> 01:13.274
ADULT ADAM:
I particularly related
to the brother dynamics.

01:13.341 --> 01:17.411
Wyatt was bullied by Chet,
and I had to live with Barry.

01:17.478 --> 01:19.347
Hey, that's my serving
of fruit for the day.

01:19.413 --> 01:21.582
Oh, then maybe you should
have some punch.

01:21.649 --> 01:22.683
Ow!

01:22.750 --> 01:23.817
Okay, morons.

01:23.884 --> 01:25.653
We're only gonna be gone
for three days.

01:25.719 --> 01:27.555
Try and be alive
when we get back.

01:27.621 --> 01:29.257
All right,
that's everything.

01:29.323 --> 01:31.259
Whoa, what's
all this stuff?

01:31.325 --> 01:33.527
When I went to college,
all I brought were some
flip-flops and a cookie.

01:33.594 --> 01:37.365
Hold on, Shmoo.
There is one thing you forgot.

01:37.431 --> 01:39.567
Time to give Mama
all the kisses.

01:39.633 --> 01:41.669
Oh, come on, dude.
Really?

01:41.735 --> 01:44.272
