like little love-acorns.

01:48.876 --> 01:50.944
No, I don't even remember
how to do it.

01:51.011 --> 01:52.813
Easy.

01:52.880 --> 01:54.615
Eskimo kiss,

01:54.682 --> 01:56.150
butterfly kiss,

01:56.217 --> 01:58.219
cheek kiss, cheek kiss,

01:58.286 --> 02:00.554
and one last kiss
for your palm

02:00.621 --> 02:03.624
to ball up
and stick in your heart.

02:03.691 --> 02:04.825
Gotcha.

02:04.892 --> 02:06.394
Well I am gonna put this
in my bag for later.

02:06.460 --> 02:09.530
Don't put my kiss
in your dark duffel bag.

02:09.597 --> 02:11.299
Take it out and put it
in your heart.

02:11.365 --> 02:12.766
Stick my kiss
in your heart.

02:12.833 --> 02:14.935
I don't want the kiss, Mom.
Okay, okay. Stop.

02:15.002 --> 02:17.104
I will take your precious kiss
out of the dark bag

02:17.171 --> 02:18.672
and put it in my heart.

02:18.739 --> 02:19.940
Fake out. It's gone.

02:20.007 --> 02:22.075
No! I caught it, and I'm
throwing it back to you.

02:22.142 --> 02:23.577
No, take it back.
You take it.

02:23.644 --> 02:24.845
Take this kiss, Mom.
You keep it.

02:24.912 --> 02:26.146
I'm not going to college
with a kiss.

02:26.214 --> 02:27.014
