Point is, I know it goes

03:13.861 --> 03:15.329
against everything
you stand for,

03:15.396 --> 03:17.231
but you have
to say goodbye.

03:17.931 --> 03:19.767
Bye. Bye, now.

03:19.833 --> 03:21.201
Ta-ta.

03:21.269 --> 03:22.703
See you
on the flip-flop.

03:22.770 --> 03:23.971
What are you doing?

03:24.037 --> 03:25.639
