ways of saying goodbye.

03:25.706 --> 03:27.508
It's gonna be very hard
when that day comes.

03:27.575 --> 03:28.942
That day is now.
Leave that.

03:29.009 --> 03:31.044
Go get the rest of your stuff
out of the car,

03:31.111 --> 03:32.346
