You must be Erica's mother.

03:40.488 --> 03:42.290
Don't worry. Your daughter's
in great hands.

03:42.356 --> 03:44.358
Ah, that is
so good to hear.

03:44.425 --> 03:46.527
Now shut your (BLEEP) mouth
and do everything

03:46.594 --> 03:48.262
