Oh, dear.

03:48.329 --> 03:49.763
You might be
the other kids' R.A.,

03:49.830 --> 03:51.932
but when it comes to my
little pickle, you're me.

03:51.999 --> 03:55.303
It's your job to see
that she's fed, well-rested,

03:55.369 --> 03:57.070
