on the open market.

05:49.483 --> 05:50.884
Um, what is this?

05:50.951 --> 05:51.985
Your destiny.

05:52.052 --> 05:53.687
So, who amongst you
is ready to battle

05:53.754 --> 05:55.789
in a Thunderdome-like
cage match for my affection?

05:55.856 --> 05:57.391
Dude, what world
do you live in?

05:57.458 --> 05:59.159
You're, like,
a 2 at best.

05:59.226 --> 06:00.861
ADULT ADAM: Naturally,
Barry was delighted
by the flirtation

06:00.928 --> 06:03.664
