06:41.201 --> 06:43.437
I've penciled you in for
a daily display of dominance

06:43.504 --> 06:45.573
and humiliation
to boost my visibility

06:45.639 --> 06:48.175
in front of the more
popular, meaner kids.

06:48.241 --> 06:49.610
